Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a pickled plum in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're the sun, Tsumugu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told I couldn't go up to the surface by myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still always looked up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the ocean, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and ever so distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It shone down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It sparked a flame in me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and made my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
