Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's really quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it always this quiet at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always thought everyone would be more restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because it's right before the hibernation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because the saltflake snow has piled up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it was decided that Namiji Middle School would be closed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we started going to school on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was when it began.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let anyone see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're showing it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manaka had said that,\N but she showed Tsumugu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, restless ripples began to form in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It grew stormy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt like a ship adrift in the turbulent waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.14,How the Fuck Do I Typeset This,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\shad4\bord0\fax0.2\fscx131\fscy67\c&H714C8A&\4c&H000000&\4a&H56&\frz341.1\pos(1041,196)}G{\c&H3852A4&}e{\c&H3C6B43&}t
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm sure it's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone cares for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even though some of us \Ndon't realize our own feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or know what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And even though someone cares about us,\N we're unable to notice it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or respond in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're thrown about by the waves and battered against the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it takes everything we have to stay afloat\N as we try to make it to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, {\i0}because{\i1} of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for showing up so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of glad you were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you out on a walk?{no one ever goes out for a swim, huh}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon does look pretty tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,About earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.20,Alternative,,0,0,0,,So—{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I just blurted all that stuff out earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda got swept up in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood rushed to my head, and I just said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I haven't really grown up after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... really do love you, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, and you're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing I'm sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chisaki, Kaname, and Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, Miuna, and Sayu... even Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not you love me in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll always be precious to me, \Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So... What were you going to say before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun, wave the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave it as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, no one will get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out, Dad, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize today's the day of the hibernation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't stay out too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best to stay awake until you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You were secretly eating while you were up there, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think we wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the festival goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So they gave you their blessing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They said to do my best at the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everything go okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our first big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to work things out in the end, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You were working really hard to prepare for the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just doing whatever I could to spend more time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Chisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have had too much on your mind \Nwith your feelings for Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did confess to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I haven't forgotten, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do end up going to sleep, \Nand then we wake up at different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always love you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname...{time for ecco the dolphin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And we took our time getting up here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the days to be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are unbelievable, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. She might be the most unbelievable one of us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't complimenting me... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandma was practically falling out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all quite lively for people who are meant to be getting ready to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to pay our respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to participate in the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it'd be pointless, \Nbut we're gonna do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can change on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the four of you are a different story.\N Maybe you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you grew up before I even realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing more to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You set this in motion yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you follow it through to the end,\N no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Akari to lead a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.62,The Club of the Kettle,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&HBEBD99&\fscx80\fscy80\pos(712,98)\frx4\fry0\org(601,99)\b1}Boatdrift Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened,\N but who knew it'd get this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you being all serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing us! Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are you planning to guide everyone in the Boatdrift Ceremony dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man of the sea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And men of the sea wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,those!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm {\i1}from{\i0} the sea,\N but I'm not a man of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. We're taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops. Could you turn this guy into a proper man of the sea too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo-Mom... M-Mo-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that'd make Akari-san really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You... think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna! You won't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing, Miuna! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna, Itaru-san, thank you so much for listening to my selfish wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be together forever now anyway, right, {replace}Aka-cha{Aka}—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is just for show,\N but if I look at you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to let you \Ngo marry the sea god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't look! I'll never look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Daddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this is over, I have something\N I want to tell you.{rip one of these two}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later then, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.43,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.05\blur0.8\fscx158\fscy158\c&H370A08&\frz356.9\frx0\fry2\pos(974,370)\1a&H2A&}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being guided by spirit fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you watching, Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may only be mere drops in this vast ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the people of the ocean \Nand the people of the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are all doing their best to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all want to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all want to stay with the people who are precious to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Sea God, if you're really out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hear our wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the sea god really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...come to take Akari-san?!{HEY WASN'T THIS A GREAT IDEA}{Akari: "...Shit."}{more like Akari: "Abandon ship!" see next cut}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like my body won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}! What's going o—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I am but a scale of the sea god.{at the end of the day}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we don't get up to the surface soon, Tsumugu-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The bridge pier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No!{can't jump in after him, eh}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari-san has people waiting for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is precious to someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't take them away \Nfrom their loved ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have to take someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me instead!{why not just continue swimming upwards >.>}{take my waifu. onegai.}{too much sense it makes}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the boat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari!
